    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Hellish Rebuke</strong> (Level 1 Evocation)</p><p>You point your finger, and the creature that damaged you is momentarily surrounded by hellish flames. The creature must make a dexterity saving throw. It takes 2d10 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d10 for each slot level above 1st.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 reaction | <strong>Range:</strong> 60 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Warlock</em></p>",
